Plot: A young FBI agent disappears while investigating a murder miles from Twin Peaks that may be related to the future murder of Laura Palmer; the last week of the life of Laura Palmer is chronicled.
Title: Twin Peaks: Fire Walk with Me
Writer: David Lynch, Robert Engels, Mark Frost (television series Twin Peaks), David Lynch (television series Twin Peaks)
Actors: Sheryl Lee, Ray Wise, Mädchen Amick, Dana Ashbrook
tomatoConsensus: For better or worse, Twin Peaks: Fire Walk With Me is every bit as strange and twisted as you'd expect from David Lynch.
